main event: A witness observed a bright, luminous, disk-shaped object in the sky over Far Rockaway, New York on August 10, 1965.
interesting points: The object was under no apparent control and had no visible means of propulsion.
The object was hovering almost motionless in the sky before suddenly moving upward and gaining speed, but did not disappear abruptly.
The witness had never seen anything like this object before and felt it was distinctly different from any typical aircraft.
The witness reported the sighting to the Air Force's Project Blue Book program, which investigated UFOs.
